                            <comment id="12798" author="markstgodard" created="Thu, 31 Mar 2005 13:58:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Juergen,&lt;br/&gt;
I don&apos;t know if this has been looked at yet, however I have attached a patch to implement the Hibernate event listener configuration.&lt;br/&gt;
As per my javadoc in the attached patch, event listeners are configured at the LocalSessionFactoryBean by setting the &apos;eventListener&apos; property. Keys are the event type (i.e. &quot;load&quot;, &quot;save-update&quot;, &quot;auto-flush&quot;,etc&quot;, and the values are the actual event listeners.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;i.e.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example: &lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;bean id=&quot;sessionFactory&quot; class=&quot;org.springframework.orm.hibernate3.LocalSessionFactoryBean&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   . . .&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;property name=&quot;eventListeners&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
     &amp;lt;map&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
       &amp;lt;entry key=&quot;load&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;ref local=&quot;myLoadEventListener&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
       &amp;lt;/entry&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
       &amp;lt;entry key=&quot;save-update&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;ref local=&quot;mySaveOrUpdateEventListener&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
       &amp;lt;/entry&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
     &amp;lt;/map&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; &amp;lt;bean id=&quot;myLoadEventListener&quot; class=&quot;foo.bar.MyLoadEventListener&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &amp;lt;bean id=&quot;mySaveOrUpdateEventListener&quot; class=&quot;foo.bar.MySaveOrUpdateEventListener&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note: There are a few different Hibernate event listener interfaces, the above is just an example.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please let me know if you have any questions or if you need anything else.&lt;br/&gt;
Cheers&lt;br/&gt;
Mark&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12799" author="markstgodard" created="Thu, 31 Mar 2005 13:59:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;org.springframework.orm.hibernate3.LocalSessionFactoryBean patch to enable configuration of Hibernate event listeners.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12818" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Mon, 4 Apr 2005 00:01:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for pointing this out! I&apos;ve added an &quot;eventListeners&quot; bean property to LocalSessionFactoryBean, accepting listener type/object pairs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
